      • getParent

        public AnnotatedElement getParent()
        Description copied from interface: Injectee
        If this Injectee is in a constructor this will return the constructor being injected into. If this Injectee is in a method this will return the method being injected into. If this injectee represents a field, this will return the field being injected into. This injectee may be neither (it may be the result of a lookup with ServiceLocator.getInjecteeDescriptor(Injectee)) in which case this will return null.
        Specified by:
        getParent in interface Injectee
        Returns:
        The parent of the injectee, which may be null
